        "To begin, we try a model that acts as if\n",
        "the data satisfied a $\\tau^{\\textrm{th}}$-order Markov condition,\n",
        "and thus predicts $x_t$ using only the past $\\tau$ observations.\n",
        "[*Thus for each time step we have an example\n",
