      "source": [
        "This figure is quite exciting.\n",
        "First, beyond unigram words, sequences of words\n",
        "also appear to be following Zipf's law,\n",
        "albeit with a smaller exponent\n",
        "$\\alpha$ in @eq-zipf_law,\n",
